                     <interp inst="t18420509-1550-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18420509-1550-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>for feloniously forging and uttering, on the <rs id="t18420509-cd-108" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18420509-1550-offence-1 t18420509-cd-108"></join>12th of February</rs>, an acquittance and receipt for 4<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 13<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., with intent to defraud <persName id="t18420509-name-661" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18420509-name-661" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
